{"tid":420121,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇大種乞衣買快運俾人取消但買無得取消既酒店","createTime":"2017-10-01T06:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T12:26:04.000Z","uid":65328,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"78e451384db1407c29cfe56d9d175b2045a88816","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"有冇大種乞衣買快運俾人取消但買無得取消既酒店？ <br />\n<br />\n我只想講句<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵你死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔睇新聞， 或心存僥倖， 或貪小便宜忽略風險， 慳左少少錢， 大時大節買快運， 再買無得取消既酒店， 真係抵你死"},{"pid":"7aa1d60d2cdc9c2fc423a790105c62c8f9832953","tid":420121,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15350f3b11c5daaa8fac68a25c0cc60729bd1dea","tid":420121,"uid":10975,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"買廉航預左佢取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廉航唔撚係航？<br />\n咁都有得鬧貪平，根本唔係貪唔貪既問題，大家都飛到去目的地，比多幾千買因航買埋佢啲垃圾服務好抵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主咁唔貪平係咪次次都坐頭等？"},{"pid":"9bfb2c1a051aceafad522b6123b7af7ab4eeef80","tid":420121,"uid":123774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"你係咪好窮成世仔未去旅行？<br />\n連訂廉航既人都要妒忌"},{"pid":"7b2e1c3a20a11a2b1eea1c248ac386336b2fde12","tid":420121,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"風險風你老母險<br />\n估到佢會取消？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8e61d7a1c68fa6fe5949c30d2a72fd3a101947","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買廉航預左佢取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廉航唔撚係航？<br />\n咁都有得鬧貪平，根本唔係貪唔貪既問題，大家都飛到去目的地，比多幾千買因航買埋佢啲垃圾服務好抵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主咁唔貪平係咪次次都坐頭等？</blockquote><br />\n你文盲定弱智定梅毒上腦， 講明快運， 你講咩廉航"},{"pid":"f49a1dd78c3347290c0647c512bc50b79b2ba4e7","tid":420121,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買廉航預左佢取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廉航唔撚係航？<br />\n咁都有得鬧貪平，根本唔係貪唔貪既問題，大家都飛到去目的地，比多幾千買因航買埋佢啲垃圾服務好抵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主咁唔貪平係咪次次都坐頭等？</blockquote><br />\n你文盲定弱智定梅毒上腦， 講明快運， 你講咩廉航</blockquote><br />\n改撚番左快運囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩唔岩心水呀<br />\n有野就講啦戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"db7e80093d1758d6fa703ea936dba8da79f6534c","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪好窮成世仔未去旅行？<br />\n連訂廉航既人都要妒忌</blockquote><br />\n又係你隻大種乞衣， 妒忌你買快運俾人取消航班？<br />\n<br />\n你如果無梅毒上腦， 實記得幾個月前我已經同你嘈好多次唔好買快運， 點呀， 你係咪唔聽買左快運中左招大種乞衣"},{"pid":"bde1db433c6e75a706226d8cf41b99ef499e6a95","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風險風你老母險<br />\n估到佢會取消？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快運取消洗估？ 近一年大把post不斷講快運好唔掂"},{"pid":"1a38970132bb4de7d5c8eca04e26f403300a30dd","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買廉航預左佢取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廉航唔撚係航？<br />\n咁都有得鬧貪平，根本唔係貪唔貪既問題，大家都飛到去目的地，比多幾千買因航買埋佢啲垃圾服務好抵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主咁唔貪平係咪次次都坐頭等？</blockquote><br />\n你文盲定弱智定梅毒上腦， 講明快運， 你講咩廉航</blockquote><br />\n改撚番左快運囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩唔岩心水呀<br />\n有野就講啦戇鳩仔</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩得過你我講快運你走去講廉航"},{"pid":"bec73c3ecf67df70a3251d2605129d34abe46b71","tid":420121,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"平嘢永遠係最貴嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8264785d2469e04019238927d822ddc7000f660d","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"7月我開左好多post屌班大種乞衣唔好再搭快運<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/376220/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/376220/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"43b7b1abc5df90013b075ae29c91eed435ba1bbe","tid":420121,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風險風你老母險<br />\n估到佢會取消？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同紅白藍bb兩隻大種乞衣有冇俾快運取消航班"},{"pid":"ad016de1577721e1948c1220ef06ce559b7f49a4","tid":420121,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>風險風你老母險<br />\n估到佢會取消？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同紅白藍bb兩隻大種乞衣有冇俾快運取消航班</blockquote><br />\n明知間野咁仆街都仲要買, 而家飛唔到咪抵撚死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb377afe79534df4e97ed40dc691ccf90750fb1","tid":420121,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re